What is (CORS) Cross-Origin Resource Sharing ?
What does "other-domain" means?
a different scheme (HTTP or HTTPS)
a different domain 
a different port
Why do we need CORS?
Facebook was found to be vulnerable to such a CORS attack.
One domain + port combination cannot read the response to a request from

How to allow CORS in react.js?
Using proxy in package.json file.
Add the API part to package.json file.
Then make request :-




React.useEffect(() => {
    axios
        .get('api/profile/')
        .then(function (response) {
            console.log(response);
        })
        .catch(function (error) {
            console.log(error);
        });
});

